}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== "WPIA104G_V00 109-101-8600" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos.
WPM55AG v1.2 serial numbers appear to start with '''MDM2'''.
This device may use U-NII-2 channels but does not implement DFS since it predates the FCC requirements.
